{"tid":1127911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（物管請教）比裝修佬大鳩我，點搞？","createTime":"2019-04-27T12:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T13:06:08.000Z","uid":171277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"633ed310ea216707a99c90a8643bbe8eb557fd0b","tid":1127911,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"話說小弟就管緊舊樓<br />\n<br />\n有個單位裝修緊，個師傅話大廈喉管老化，好易爆，怕係裝修期間震爆條咸水喉，所以要我第二日停咸水（一停就停全座既相同單位）<br />\n<br />\n我拒絕，話要七日通知（其實有冇明文寫明要7日通知？）<br />\n<br />\n佢就話book晒師傅，book晒期，唔會delay，通知就通知左我，到時唔停水又震爆左搞到d咸水周圍噴就我後果自負。<br />\n<br />\n今日又黎單食水喉又係咁<br />\n<br />\n師兄們點搞好？"},{"pid":"9fec261ba297a18ff5480ac3f9eb0730a5e2a6f8","tid":1127911,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11de8a74f1351986a7b9d086cd071ef184fd2ad0","tid":1127911,"uid":172570,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"你話停就停<br />\n唔洗時間通知同申請咩<br />\n有咩事都係佢負責<br />\n按程序做野"},{"pid":"50b1cba5d02262631368a56b7b2de558c1ae623e","tid":1127911,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"佢冇書面通知就當佢冇通知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e113fc3f519f8080c5e01f5e4276d05c58ed1341","tid":1127911,"uid":13645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾咁都俾人大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b712c63c23896575bbbfbc30cf14e08a07dac1","tid":1127911,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e113fc3f519f8080c5e01f5e4276d05c58ed1341","tid":1127911,"uid":13645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"